sequenceDiagram
    actor Cliente
    participant UI as RegisterScreen\nmobile/lib/register_screen.dart
    participant API as users.py -> user_controller.py
    participant S as user_service.py\nregister_user()
    participant R as user_repository.py\nUserRepository
    participant T1 as Tabla usuario
    participant T2 as Tabla rol
    participant T3 as Tabla rol_usuario
    participant T4 as Tabla cliente/taller

    Cliente->>UI: 1. Completa formulario de registro
    UI->>API: 1.1 POST /api/v1/usuarios/registro
    API->>S: 1.2 register_user(payload)
    S->>R: 1.3 get_user_by_email(correo)
    R->>T1: 1.4 SELECT usuario por correo
    S->>R: 1.5 create_user(...)
    R->>T1: 1.6 INSERT usuario
    S->>R: 1.7 get_or_create_role(...)
    R->>T2: 1.8 SELECT/INSERT rol
    S->>R: 1.9 assign_role_to_user(...)
    R->>T3: 2.0 INSERT rol_usuario
    S->>R: 2.1 create_cliente_profile() o create_taller_profile()
    R->>T4: 2.2 INSERT cliente o taller
    S-->>API: 2.3 Registro exitoso
    API-->>UI: 2.4 201 Created
    UI-->>Cliente: 2.5 Mostrar mensaje de exito